name: Xiastore - Electronics
description:
Xiastore is a unique template design that follows the latest design and marketing trends. With our template, you do not have to think about how to properly implement the design. All pages and user steps are taken into account. You can customize and change the content for any of your needs.


Functions


- 10+ full layer Adobe Photoshop .PSD and Figma files


- Designed with responsiveness in mind


- Clean, modern design


- Well organized layers make it very easy to update


- All fonts used in templates are available in Google Font.
